prompts.user:
Evaluate the health of this project:

Project: {projectName}
Description: {projectDescription}
Status: {projectStatus}
Completion: {completionPercentage}%

Tasks:
{taskSummary}

Milestones:
{milestoneSummary}

Check for:
1. Stale tasks (in_progress for too long relative to estimate)
2. Blocked tasks with no resolution path
3. Critical path drift (will the project miss its estimated completion?)
4. Agent errors or unresponsive agents
5. Upcoming milestone deadlines at risk

Return JSON:
{
  "overallHealth": "healthy|at_risk|critical",
  "findings": [
    {
      "type": "stale_task|blocker|critical_path_drift|agent_error|milestone_reached",
      "severity": "info|warning|critical",
      "taskId": "optional task ID",
      "message": "Description of the finding",
      "suggestedAction": "What to do about it"
    }
  ],
  "recommendations": ["Actionable recommendation strings"],
  "estimatedCompletionAt": 0
}
